<plot>The world in Alien Entity looks familiar with the exception of two strange entities, which move curiously while exploring the environment. They manage to switch on an old video game console and start playing. The interest in the game decreases after a third entity has entered the room. Combining black-and-white backgrounds with colored creatures and game animation this short is an homage to the early days of video games.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?030082</url></doc>
